to run this in conjunction with st-mona:
1. run st-mona as normal
2. go to the control subdirectory 
3. ./control.py -i <infile> -o <outfile>
	infile = the output of st-mona
	outfile = name of the final output file you want
4. when geant starts, go /run/beamOn x
	x = number of events you ran in st-mona
5. that should do it
